OL,3,CThree staff members at care home
OL,4,Carrested after allegations of violence
OL,6,FThree members of staff at a care home
OL,7,Fin Devon have been arrested after
OL,8,Fallegations of violence and neglect of
OL,9,Fresidents.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to a care home on
OL,12,FBrixington Lane, in Exmouth, believed
OL,13,Fto be Knappe Cross Care Centre.
OL,15,FThey said they are working with the
OL,16,Fcouncil and Care Quality Commission to
OL,17,Fmake sure any inappropriate activity
OL,18,Fis dealt with promptly.
OL,20,FThe three members of staff have been
OL,21,Freleased on bail.
