OL,6,FThe care homeowners said they are
OL,7,Fcooperating fully with authorities and
OL,8,Fthat they remain fully committed to
OL,9,Fthe highest standards of care.
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall Police said they
OL,12,Fwere notified recently following
OL,13,Fconcerns regarding the care of
OL,14,Fresidents at a care home in Brixington
OL,15,FLane, in Exmouth.
OL,17,FOfficers have commenced a criminal
OL,18,Finvestigation regarding activity at
OL,19,Fthe home.
